{"tid":1766044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"攬炒大捷 10月零售貨值按年跌24.3%，高過預期","createTime":"2019-12-02T09:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T09:59:56.000Z","uid":189799,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab7c6688d1cdb668f6cdd7e7049da6b2979280e","tid":1766044,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"￼查看<br />\n<br />\nnow 新聞 - 24小時直播<br />\n<br />\nPCCW Media Limited<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n10月零售銷售大跌24.3%　跌幅破紀錄<br />\n<br />\n36分鐘前&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】本港10月零售銷售遜預期單月跌幅是有紀錄以來最大。<br />\n<br />\n10月零售銷售貨值301億元，跌百分之24.3，連跌九個月，貨量跌逾兩成六，銷貨值及貨量均遜預期。<br />\n<br />\n按分部來看，珠寶首飾、鐘表及名貴禮物銷售貨值，跌幅最大，跌逾四成二。鞋類、有關製品及其他衣物配件﹑服裝、藥物及化妝品，均下跌逾三成。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示零售銷售十月持續大幅下滑，是由於本地社會事件涉及的暴力增加，嚴重打擊消費情緒，並干擾旅遊業及與消費相關的活動。政府稱，停止社會暴力事件和恢復社會秩序是零售復甦的關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=371988&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371988%26refer%3D&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=b0f85ff4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371988%26refer%3D&h=b873a26c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=371988&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"35293da44cb94aae73fc61772e5ab2637700e379","tid":1766044,"uid":293227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:51:17.000Z","msg":"成績表"},{"pid":"b08b925c4742f5c01cc2bef37977e5be1e1f280c","tid":1766044,"uid":4139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"出街聽到廢老話點解仲要搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話撚到明唔回應就繼續攬炒嫁啦 一齊冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /